# Design System — Traffic AI (UX Pilot v1)

Always follow `docs/design-system.md` when building or editing UI.

## Quick rules

- Page background: `bg-[var(--surface-bg)]` or `.ui-surface`
- Cards: `.ui-card` or `DsCard` — never ad-hoc `border-slate-200 bg-white`
- Primary CTA (sync, create, save): `.ui-btn-primary` (amber gradient)
- AI / Agency Brain actions: `.ui-btn-brand` (violet gradient)
- Secondary actions: `.ui-btn-secondary`
- Page titles: `font-heading text-[var(--text-main)]`
- Body/labels: `text-[var(--text-dim)]` / `text-[var(--text-dimmer)]`
- Links: `.ui-link` (violet) or `.ui-link-amber`
- Sidebar stays dark `#0a0f14`; active nav item uses amber, not cyan/violet
- Tables: header `--surface-thead`, hover `--row-hover`, use `DsTableShell` when possible
- KPI cards: `.kpi-card-hover`, colored metric values, `DsTrendBadge` for deltas
- Agency Brain blocks: `.ui-brain-shelf` or `--brain-shelf-bg`

## Imports

Prefer `@/design-system` components over one-off styled divs for headers, badges, cards, and tables.

Reference mock: `uxpilot-export/src/` (do not import from there in app code).
